init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I started scanning down the list of names and my eyes stopped on the very first entry.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Which was probably the first step to realizing that this wasn't a ranking at all.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My wife and I would take our kids to the park, than have lunch together.
